headline: Does The Recent Dip Make Yum Brands Attractive After Global Expansion And Digital Growth News
summary: Wondering if Yum! Brands at around $143.89 is a tasty opportunity or just fully priced fast food? You are not alone. Let's unpack what the market is really paying for here. The stock is down about 3.1% over the last week and 2.9% over the last month, but it is still up 7.7% year to date and 47.0% over five years.
